snippet.title: DreamDoll - You know My body (feat. Capella Gray) [Behind the Scenes]
snippet.description:
🔔 Subscribe to the official channel: https://smarturl.it/DreamDollSubscribe

Behind the Scenes video for “You Know My body”.
Stream/Download 'You Know My body': 
https://dreamdoll.lnk.to/YouKnowMyBody

DreamDoll Complete Dollection on Spotify:
https://open.spotify.com/playlist/4N1...

Follow DreamDoll:
https://www.theoriginaldreamdoll.com
https://twitter.com/dreamdoll
https://instagram.com/dreamdoll
https://facebook.com/realdreamdoll

CREDITS:
Director:  Sara Lacombe
Producer: David Wept
Production Company: Noire Creative

Lyrics:

We ain't even gonna speak about it
I’ve seen it all mine, you know my body (you know my body)
You know my body (you know my body)
Heard It all before (uh)
So just gotta make sure you know my body (you know my body)
You know my body (you know my body yeah)

Uh, if you heard what the F I did
Then you would understand why my pockets gettin’ vesti big
What my ex didn’t do then the next guy did
Cause I don’t even stick around if the sex not lit
I admin that I like you or whatever
That's when you got a check on me like I was a Nike or whatever
My phone don’t ring its curtains
For you ain't that b*** so make sure that the s*** is worth it
And I don’t even got to trip I got to cover him if he wildin’
I work way too hard for them Birkins in my closet
Its Dream b*** don’t you ever forget
I’m really going to give you something that you’ll never forget

We ain't even gonna speak about it
I’ve seen it all mine, you know my body (you know my body)
You know my body (you know my body yeah)
Heard It all before (uh)
So just gotta make sure, you know my body (you know my body)
You know my body (you know my body yeah)

I hate when I get out of line
Or step out of pocket
Like when I’m pissed off I throw your s*** out my closet
If a n**** play me then a n**** done up
Cause everyday a new b*** tryna get the one up
I know all the tricks,
I know all the games,
I got all the facts,
I think y’all all the same
But hold up,
I need a n**** who’s gone always show up
A n**** just like my money he gone never fold up
Cause I’m too much of a bad b**** to f*** with a loser
I pulled up in a Lamb he pulled up in a Uber
See the dream on the block or I’m up in Aruba
If a n*** gotta pick then n**** gonna choose her

We ain't even gonna speak about it
I've seen it all mine, you know my body (you know my body)
You know my body (you know my body yeah)
Heard It all before (uh)
So just gotta make sure, you know my body (you know my body)
You know my body (you know my body yeah)

She just want to freak with me, OG
She don’t want nobody got a pre
She don’t wanna party, she just want to stay the night
And make love all night

#DreamDoll #CapellaGray #YouKnowMyBody
